text: John Hayward (born before 1530 – died by 1572), of Dorchester, Dorset, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Dorchester in 1558. ==References== Category:Year of death missing Category:English MPs 1558 Category:Members of the Parliament of England for Dorchester Category:Year of birth uncertain
title: John Hayward (MP for Dorchester)
